   <text>
      <body>
         <pb facs="1872_02_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Buchheister_Edo_1.tif" n="1"/>
         <p>
            <seg rend="right">
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00542">Yeddo</placeName> d: <date when="1872-02-05">5
                            Februar 1872</date>
               </hi>
            </seg>
            <lb/>
            <seg rend="center">Herren <hi rend="latintype">
                  <orgName type="firm" ref="K01004">L. Kniffler+C<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>
                  </orgName>.<lb/>
                  <placeName ref="K00525">Yokohama</placeName>
               </hi>
            </seg>
            <lb/> In Antwort auf Ihr<lb/>
            <date when="1872-02-05">heutiges</date> Telegramm bitte ich<lb/> Sie das <term type="logistic" ref="K01515">Connossement</term> für die <term type="goods" ref="K01638">Rifles</term>
            <lb/> an Herrn <hi rend="latintype">
               <orgName type="firm" ref="K01011">Bourjau Hübener + C<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>
               </orgName>
            </hi> zu<lb/> senden + die Versicherung für<lb/>
            <term type="commercial" ref="K01508">$</term>
            <measure type="currency" quantity="3500" unit="mex$">3500</measure> zu
                besorgen.<lb/> Ich werde wahrscheinlich<lb/> morgen Abend nach <placeName ref="K00525">Jokohama</placeName>
            <lb/> gehen &amp; mir dann erlauben, <lb/> bei Ihnen vorzusprechen<lb/>
            <seg rend="right">Ergebenst<lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <persName ref="K00056">
                     <unclear>J. J.</unclear> Buchheister</persName>
               </hi>
            </seg>
         </p>
         <pb facs="1872_02_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Buchheister_Edo_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p>
            <add style="writingMode: vertical-lr; textOrientation: sideways-right" resp="other" place="marginRight">1872<lb/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <placeName ref="K00542">Yedo</placeName>
                  <date when="1872-02-05">5 Febr.</date>
                  <lb/>
                  <persName ref="K00056">J. J. Buchheister</persName>
                  <lb/> R<hi rend="underline">
                     <date when="1872-02-05">5 Febr.</date>
                  </hi>
                  <lb/> bwt. <date when="1872-02-28">28 Feb.</date>
                  <lb/> U<lb/> RC</hi>
            </add>
         </p>
      </body>
   </text>
   <text type="translation">
      <body>
         <pb facs="1872_02_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Buchheister_Edo_1.tif" n="1"/>
         <p>Yeddo, 5th February 1872<lb/>Messrs. L. Kniffler + Co.<lb/>Yokohama<lb/> In answer to
                your <lb/>telegram from today I would like to ask <lb/>you to send the bill of
                lading for the <lb/>rifles to Messrs. Bourjau Hübener + Co <lb/>+ to procure the
                insurance over <lb/>$ 3,500. <lb/>I will probably go to Yokohama<lb/>tomorrow
                evening <lb/>&amp; will take the liberty then <lb/>of calling on you.<lb/>Yours most
                sincerely<lb/>J. J. Buchheister</p>
         <pb facs="1872_02_05_Kniffler_Yokohama_von_Buchheister_Edo_2.tif" n="2"/>
         <p>⟨1872<lb/>Yedo 5th Feb. <lb/>J. J. [?] Buchheister <lb/>R[eceived] 5th Feb.<lb/>answ.
                28th Feb. <lb/>U<lb/>RC⟩</p>
      </body>
